---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
const posts = await getCollection('blog');
---
<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Portal de Longevidade</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
      a { color: #3498db; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
      li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Protocolos de Longevidade</h1>
    <p>Bem-vindo ao portal oficial. Abaixo, nossos protocolos atualizados:</p>
    <ul>
      {posts.map(post => (
        <li>
          <a href={`/blog/${post.id}`}>{post.data.title}</a>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </body>
</html>
